New Keepers Of The Water Towers is a heavy metal band from Stockholm .

The band was formed in 2007 by drummer Tor SjÃ¶dÃ©n and guitarist / vocalist Rasmus Booberg. 2009 they released their debut album Chronicles of the American record company Meteor City. The album consists of their two self-financed half long conductor Chronicles of the Massive Boar (2007) and The Chronicles of Iceman (2008). LP edition of The Chronicles of Iceman was released in the summer of 2010 on High Roller Records.

Their second studio album, The Calydonian Hunt was released in April 2011 at Meteor City. Third studio album, Cosmic Child, was released in 2013 on the French label Listenable Records. 


2009 - Chronicles
2011 - The Calydonian Hunt
2013 - Cosmic Child
2016 - Infernal Machine
